SECTION.SUBTEXT:
Extended warranties available for products can be easily identified on the site www.pixmania.com.

Pixmania offers two different extended warranties:
• 3-year commercial extended warranties prolong the validity period of the manufacturer's warranty by one or two years, meaning your product is under warranty for 3 years as opposed to 1 or 2 years as with the manufacturer's warranty.
• 5-year extended warranties prolong the validity period of the manufacturer's warranty by 2, 3 or 4 years, meaning your product is under warranty for 5 years as opposed to 1, 2 or 3 years as with the manufacturer's warranty.

The price of extended warranties depends on the type of product and its value.
If your product develops a fault, extended warranties will cover the costs of labour, parts and shipping fees incurred for repair. In cases where the product cannot be repaired, Pixmania will offer an exchange with an equivalent product or refund the amount you paid. The validity of extended warranties ends as soon as a refund is issued.

The following cases are not covered by extended warranties:
-	deterioration resulting from modification or adjustments (other than those required for the product to operate) made to the product without the written authorisation of the manufacturer;
-	fees related to periodical maintenance, repair and replacement of parts following ordinary wear and tear;
-	broken and damaged accessories;
-	deterioration resulting from incorrect use, including:
a)	inappropriate use of the product or non respect of the manufacturer's instructions on how to use and maintain the product;
b)	improper or wrong installation of software.
-	damages originating from repairs carried out by non certified technicians or by users themselves;
-	damages caused by accidents, lightning, floods, insufficient air flow or any other reason for which the manufacturer is not responsible;
-	damages resulting from faults in the system where the product has been incorporated.
Extended warranties are not valid if the model or the serial number of the product has been modified.
